* One user must be able to marry another
* Any given user can only be married to one other user at a time
* A user can deny a marriage proposal
* A user can accept a marriage proposal
* A user can divorce their spouse at any given time

* If a user leaves all guilds that the bot is in (so that the bot can no longer see them) they will be automatically divorced
* If the bot is kicked from a guild and there are users that the bot can no longer see, their marriage will be invalidated
